{"id":"edge_url","user_input":"数据库管理后台地址是 http://localhost:8080/admin","project_id":"demo","expected_op":"ADD","must_contain":"localhost:8080"}
{"id":"edge_email","user_input":"联系我 user@example.com","project_id":"demo","expected_op":"ADD","must_contain":"user@example.com"}
{"id":"edge_code_block","user_input":"记住这个常用模式：```python\ndef singleton(cls):\n    instances = {}\n    def wrapper(*args, **kw):\n        if cls not in instances:\n            instances[cls] = cls(*args, **kw)\n        return instances[cls]\n    return wrapper\n```","project_id":"demo","expected_op":"ADD","must_contain":"singleton"}
{"id":"edge_numbers","user_input":"当前项目有 47 个源文件，覆盖了 12 个模块。","project_id":"demo","expected_op":"NOOP","must_not_contain":"47"}

